            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features</h2>

                <ul>
                    <li>Applite can now be installed with Homebrew</li>
                    <li>New languages: French and Hungarian</li>
                    <li>New &quot;Terminals&quot; category is now available</li>
                    <li>Installed apps can now be exported to a file. Import it on another device to install all exported apps. You can find this option in the &quot;Manage Homebrew&quot; section</li>
                    <li>New &quot;Active Tasks&quot; section where you can view actively installing apps</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Known Issues</h2>

                <p>Apps installed with .pkg installers require an admin password to complete. This is not currently supported by Applite. We are working on a fix, but in the meantime, see <a href="https://aerolite.dev/applite/troubleshooting.html">Troubleshooting</a> for a possible workaround.
                </p>
            ]]>
            </description>
